    <string name="terms_body_placeholder">The terms and policies of EasyMoney will be updated when the official documents are ready. Please contact the call center for details.</string>
    <string name="terms_body">1. Scope\nThese terms apply to EasyMoney account registration, account usage, loan package browsing, loan application submission, electronic contract signing, and wallet/payment services in the application.\n\n2. User responsibilities\nYou must provide accurate information, update it when it changes, and protect your account, OTP, and biometric authentication methods. You are responsible for actions performed from a valid signed-in account.\n\n3. Profile and identity verification\nEasyMoney may request face verification, NFC chip ID scanning, or document image upload depending on the device and review flow. NFC and document upload are alternative methods; one successful document verification method is sufficient when required by the system.\n\n4. Loans and contracts\nLoan limit, term, interest, fees, repayment schedule, and payment obligations are shown before confirmation. The electronic contract becomes effective after you accept the terms, verify OTP, and complete signing in the application.\n\n5. Notifications and contact\nThe application may send notifications about application status, contracts, transactions, offers, and repayment reminders. You can change notification preferences in Settings.\n\n6. Security and data\nEasyMoney processes personal data to verify identity, review applications, manage loans, prevent fraud, and comply with legal requirements. Data is stored, transmitted, and permissioned according to system security policies.\n\n7. Support\nFor account, contract, loan, or transaction support, please contact hotline %1$s or official support channels in the application.</string>
    <string name="hotline_number">19001234</string>

